00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:43,040
we didn't change the velocities.

438
00:14:43,140 --> 00:14:43,260
Well,

439
00:14:43,260 --> 00:14:43,440
yes,

440
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:43,680
okay,

441
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:43,960
yes,

442
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:44,300
we did.

443
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:45,160
We did.

444
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:46,360
We rotated.

445
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,960
We rotated the velocities.

446
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:50,260
We rotated the velocities.

447
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:51,280
Okay.

448
00:14:52,020 --> 00:14:52,500
Right.

449
00:14:52,620 --> 00:14:54,120
So the velocity was a vector.

